used for He-6 beam production. U400 was used for He-6
beam acceleration.

x4codes.hlp: Secondary beam from projectile fragment separator

x4freetext: Intensity of He-6 beam was 2*10**7 part/sec. Energy
spread was 0.4 MeV.
Gold foils with the thickness from 13.5 to 50 mu-m.
MSP-144 was used for measuring the beam
energy on entering and exiting each target.
was used for measurements of gamma-quanta
activity. Efficiency was 4-5%.
Contribution of the meastable state was substacted.
